Package: RGridLocal
Type: Package
Title: Browser Spreadsheet Backed by the Local R Interpreter
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Alek", "Rutkowski", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "alek.rutkowski@gmail.com"))
Description: Runs the RGrid browser spreadsheet from localhost and evaluates spreadsheet formulas in the standard R interpreter installed on the user's machine. The browser interface and RGrid workbook import/export format remain compatible with RGrid.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports:
    httpuv,
    jsonlite,
    grDevices,
    tools,
    utils
NeedsCompilation: no
